<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>UX-Men</title>
<body>

<%- include('../../shared/components/header/header') %>


<div class="block poster">
    <div class="block__wrapper poster__wrapper">
        <h1 class="poster__title"> <span class="poster__accent">UX</span>-Men</h1>
    </div>
</div>


<section class="block story story--to-right story--gradient">
    <div class="block__wrapper">
        <article class="story__article">
            <div class="story__wrapper">
                <p class="story__text">
                    For many years people and programmers had lived in harmony.
                    <br>Without wars and code reviews.
                </p>
                <p class="story__text">
                    But once...
                </p>
                <p class="story__text">
                    ...something horrible did happen – <span class="story__text-accent">likes</span> from all social media had
                    suddenly <span class="story__text-accent">started to disappear</span>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="block story story--to-left">
    <div class="block__wrapper">
        <article class="story__article">
            <div class="story__wrapper">
                <p class="story__text">
                    And there was no possibility to like you friends’ pictures and no
                    possibility to see who appreciated your posts.   
                </p>
                <p class="story__text">
                    There was <span class="story__text-accent">none</span>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="story__row">
                <div class="story__item">
                    <img src="../../images/landing/panic.jpg" alt="image-panic" class="story__image">
                </div>
                <div class="story__item">
                    <p class="story__text">
                        The panic broke out.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story__row">
                <div class="story__item">
                    <p class="story__text">
                        The world was standing on the verge of a total collapse. 
                        <br>And this is how our story begins.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="story__item">
                    <img src="../../images/landing/collapse.jpg" alt="image-panic" class="story__image">
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="block conflict" id="particle_canvas">
    <div class="block__wrapper conflict__wrapper">
        <div class="conflict__text-wrapper">
            <div class="conflict__text-container">
                <div class="conflict__story-text story-text conflict__story-text--text1">
                    It turned our that a notorious villain <span class="conflict__story-text--decorate">Bugman</span> had edged
                    into the Internet and broken the code of likes. The bugs he had made were spreading faster
                    than a  <span class="conflict__story-text--decorate">coronavirus</span>.
                </div>
                <div class="conflict__story-text story-text conflict__story-text--text2">
                    It seemed like nothing could stop his malicious plot, but where the power of common humans ends, the job
                    for the <span class="conflict__story-text--decorate">UX-Men</span> begins.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="conflict__image-container">
                <img class="conflict__image" src="../../images/backgrounds/landing-page/bugman.png" alt="Notorious villain Bugman">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="conflict__button-container">
            <button class="button conflict__button">What is next?</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>




<section class="block team">
    <div class="block__wrapper team__container">
        <div class="team__text-container">
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text1 story-text">
                The governments around the globe gathered behind closed doors to find a solution. There was no time
                for second thoughts.
            </div>
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text2 story-text">
                It was instantly decided to create a <span class="team__story-text--decorate">Fast React Team</span> of the most powerful
                <span class="team__story-text--decorate">UX-Men</span> on Earth for this mission.
            </div>
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text3 story-text">
                To stop Bugman and ruin his plans UX-Men have to fight all bugs and go to the most <span class="team__story-text--decorate">dangerous</span> and
                <span class="team__story-text--decorate">unexplainable place</span>  of the Internet – to <span class="team__story-text--decorate">Odnoklassniki</span>, to find an intact piece of code and heal all
                other social media with it.
            </div>
            <div class="team__story-text team__story-text--text4 story-text">
                But who are they, our heroes?
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team__button-container">
            <button class="button team__button team__button--clicked">Meet The Team</button>
            <button class="button team__button">Continue reading</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="deadline">
    <div class="block__wrapper deadline__container">
        <div class="deadline__title"></div>
        <ul class="timer">
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="days" class="timer__date"></span>days</li>
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="hours" class="timer__date"></span>Hours</li>
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="minutes" class="timer__date"></span>Minutes</li>
            <li class="timer__item"><span id="seconds" class="timer__date"></span>Seconds</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="deadline__button-container">
            <button class="button deadline__button">You cannot stay aside!</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>